382
00:41:49,787 --> 00:41:51,778
My dad.

383
00:41:51,856 --> 00:41:55,417
Ha. Some dad sending his
kid out to risk his neck.

384
00:41:55,493 --> 00:41:57,120
He couldn't
come himself.

385
00:42:00,565 --> 00:42:02,658
Are you
Jewish, Alex?

386
00:42:02,733 --> 00:42:03,757
No.

387
00:42:03,835 --> 00:42:04,961
Tell me
the truth.

388
