Come on.

396
00:42:42,173 --> 00:42:46,200
It's Latin. It means
"And also with you. "

397
00:42:46,277 --> 00:42:49,713
I know. Of course I know Latin.

398
00:42:49,780 --> 00:42:52,613
Of course you do. You're
a Pole and a survivor.

399
00:42:52,683 --> 00:42:55,447
